data.description: Cozy move-in ready home across from Quentin Park in the heart of Lansing. This 4 bedroom 2 full bath home has a covered front porch, refinished hardwood floors in the living room and two first floor bedrooms. The third bedroom is upstairs and the fourth is in the basement with a new egress window. The eat-in kitchen has newer oak cabinets and appliances. There is a detached garage and the Washer and Dryer stay! Other updates include Hot Water heater and Plumbing in 2021 and AC in 2022. Taxes are Homestead but there is an active city of Lansing rental license through Dec. 2024.
